items.title: Dodgers-Phillies start time delayed by rain
items.summary: After some rain in the area late afternoon and into the early evening, tonight's Dodgers-Phillies contest at Citizens Bank Park is slated to begin at 7:30 p.m. ET.

items.title: Smith a contender for Red Sox 'pen in playoffs
items.summary: The plan was to ease Carson Smith back in his return from Tommy John surgery, and the Red Sox have done that.

items.title: Hamilton (thumb) frustrated he's still inactive
items.summary: Reds center fielder Billy Hamilton has shed the brace that immobilized his fractured left thumb, but not the disappointment over not being activated from the disabled list.
